ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: yes, although I don't think it will be offered again. a great course - with really good research opportunities.

This class is awesome and if you are lucky enough to get a spot, you should certainly take it, you'll learn a bunch and have a great time listening to Paul and the other students in the class discuss so many different topics.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I have no doubt I will use both the thinking skills and specific topics taught in this course to inform my future research. It was great!
